# Model checkpoints and tensor archives under tests/test-data are downloaded
# manually by developers (see README.md) and must never be committed. They used
# to be git-lfs golden weights; they are now external, opt-in downloads consumed
# by the Purpose=Manual tests.
*.safetensors
*.zsafetensor
*.pth
*.pt
*.onnx

# Sample images downloaded by the preprocessing scripts (e.g. make-sample-input.py).
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png

# Keep the directory scaffolding (.gitkeep) and small text sidecars tracked.
!.gitkeep
